The paper proposes a new RNN model that integrates attention mechanism into GRU for sequence learning problems. This makes it likely to belong to the arXiv sub-categories of natural language processing (cs.CL), computer vision (cs.CV), machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
